research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x)}(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + \u03a3_j \u03b3_j(x) c_j\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d U={u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0cC={c_j} \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u8865\u507f\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + \u5355 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + residual \u8865\u507f\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5148\u7b5b\u6e05\u695a\uff1a`expert_topk` \u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002r79 \u4e0e r80 \u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u628a `STAGE1_RATIO` \u4ece 0.25 \u63d0\u5230 0.5 \u4f1a\u53d8\u5dee\uff0c\u800c\u53bb\u6389 low-rank trunk \u7684 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e5f\u660e\u663e\u5f31\u4e8e matched `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u5230\u4e2d\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u91cc trunk \u4ecd\u662f\u5fc5\u8981\u7ec4\u6210\uff0c\u4e14\u66f4\u5f3a residual cleanup \u6bd4\u66f4\u9ad8 expert-stage \u9884\u7b97\u66f4\u91cd\u8981\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r76 \u4ec5\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 32 \u964d\u5230 24\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u65e2\u7136 routed-only\u3001shared-basis\u3001stage split\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca trunk-free staged \u8def\u7ebf\u90fd\u672a\u5e26\u6765\u66f4\u4f18\u7ed3\u6784\u6bb5\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 `lowrank + expert + residual` \u8fd9\u6761\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5f3a\u517c\u5bb9\u4e3b\u7ebf\u8fd8\u80fd\u5426\u4ec5\u901a\u8fc7\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u7f29\u5fc5\u8981 trunk \u5bbd\u5ea6\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u8d28\u91cf\u7684\u540c\u65f6\u628a total_cost \u518d\u5f80\u5de6\u63a8\u4e00\u5c0f\u6bb5\uff0c\u5e76\u5f62\u6210\u6bd4 r76 \u66f4\u7ecf\u6d4e\u7684\u65b0 Pareto \u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:25:    "self_review": "\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u8f6e\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u7ea6\u675f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r76 \u53ea\u6539 `TRUNK_RANK`\u3002\u8fd9\u6bd4\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u4e0a\u626b `STAGE1_RATIO`\u3001\u56de\u5230 `expert_topk`/`factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u6216\u7ee7\u7eed\u5c55\u5f00 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u66f4\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u8bc1\u636e\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6700\u8fd1\u56db\u8f6e\u5df2\u7ecf\u5206\u522b\u5426\u5b9a\u4e86 shared-basis\u3001routed-only lookup-budget\u3001higher stage1 budget\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca trunk-free staged \u8fd9\u56db\u6761\u89e3\u91ca\uff1b\u73b0\u5728\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u91cc\u5fc5\u8981 trunk \u5bbd\u5ea6\u5230\u5e95\u8fd8\u80fd\u538b\u591a\u5c11\u3002\u9009\u62e9 24 \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u8df3\u5230 16\uff0c\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u5148\u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u66f4\u5e73\u6ed1\u7684\u5de6\u79fb probe\uff0c\u964d\u4f4e\u628a trunk \u538b\u8fc7\u5934\u800c\u5bfc\u81f4\u7ed3\u8bba\u53ea\u5269\u201c\u660e\u663e\u53d8\u5dee\u201d\u7684\u98ce\u9669\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:64:    "self_review": "\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u8f6e\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u7ea6\u675f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r76 \u53ea\u6539 `TRUNK_RANK`\u3002\u8fd9\u6bd4\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u4e0a\u626b `STAGE1_RATIO`\u3001\u56de\u5230 `expert_topk`/`factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u6216\u7ee7\u7eed\u5c55\u5f00 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u66f4\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u8bc1\u636e\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6700\u8fd1\u56db\u8f6e\u5df2\u7ecf\u5206\u522b\u5426\u5b9a\u4e86 shared-basis\u3001routed-only lookup-budget\u3001higher stage1 budget\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca trunk-free staged \u8fd9\u56db\u6761\u89e3\u91ca\uff1b\u73b0\u5728\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u91cc\u5fc5\u8981 trunk \u5bbd\u5ea6\u5230\u5e95\u8fd8\u80fd\u538b\u591a\u5c11\u3002\u9009\u62e9 24 \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u8df3\u5230 16\uff0c\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u5148\u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u66f4\u5e73\u6ed1\u7684\u5de6\u79fb probe\uff0c\u964d\u4f4e\u628a trunk \u538b\u8fc7\u5934\u800c\u5bfc\u81f4\u7ed3\u8bba\u53ea\u5269\u201c\u660e\u663e\u53d8\u5dee\u201d\u7684\u98ce\u9669\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0160.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍明确不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r159 已在 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 下把 total_cost 压到约 0.20x，但 FVU 回升到 0.1551；当前最有信息量的问题不再是继续压更小 active path，而是这条更轻 expert 子库分支是否主要受 deployment lookup 限制。唯一主假设是：相对 r159 仅把 `K` 从 64 提到 80，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_expert_topk`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，可以把 deployment 从约 0.06x 提到约 0.08x、combined cost 控制在约 0.21x，若 FVU 能明显优于 r159 并逼近或优于当前 0.22x 锚点 0.1464，就说明 width=160 这条更轻 shared+routed 子线仍值得继续作为 `<0.25x` 主线推进。","summary":"以 r159 为 reference，保持当前更轻的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 配方不变，只改 `K=80`。这是一轮严格留在 `<0.25x` 主战场的 matched-cost deployment probe，直接测试 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 这条更轻 shared+routed 子线是否主要受 lookup budget 限制，并争取在约 0.21x 处形成比现有 0.20x/0.22x anchors 更好的新段。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"相对 r159 只改一个 env 参数 `K`，满足单变量原则。当前策略明确要求把预算聚焦在 `<0.25x`，因此优先回答这条已验证可行的轻量 shared+routed 子线能否在相近成本下打败现有 low-cost anchors，比回到 >0.4x 中成本结构或新开天然偏重的 family 更合适。之所以选 `K=80` 而不是继续压 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或切到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，是因为 r159 已把 width 压到 160 且仍可行，而 r114 已证明继续压 active experts 会显著伤害质量；当前更高信息量的是判断 width=160 是否 deployment-limited。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"80"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r159 已把 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 推到约 0.20x total_cost，FVU=0.1551，形成新的更左低成本 anchor。","相对 r159 把 `K` 从 64 提到 80 时，selection cost 基本不变，deployment 约从 0.06x 升到 0.08x，combined cost 约 0.21x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也仍处于本轮主战场 `<0.25x`。","当前 `<0.25x` 区域最强已知锚点仍是 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 的 0.24x / FVU 0.1397；本轮的核心问题是更轻 width=160 子线能否通过少量增加 lookup budget 在更低总成本下逼近或超过它。","本轮不需要代码修改；`K`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 与 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 wiring 已在历史轮次中稳定生效。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=80` 把 width=160 子线明显压到接近或优于当前 0.22x 锚点，则下一轮应以本轮为 reference，只改 `K=96`，完成这条更轻 shared+routed 子线在 `<0.25x` 带内的 deployment knee 定位。","如果 `K=80` 只带来有限改善，则说明 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 更像 width-limited 而非 lookup-limited；下一轮应回到 r159 或本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 回升一档，而不是继续堆 `K`。","如果 `K=80` 仍明显落后于同成本 anchors，则可更明确地下调 width=160 子线优先级，下一轮改做 low-cost matched architecture probe，例如直接对照 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 是否能在同成本带提供更优质量。"],"reference_round":159}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0150.json:44:      "\u6700\u8fd1\u4e09\u6761 fresh \u7ed3\u6784\u5bf9\u7167\u7ed3\u679c\u5206\u522b\u662f r147 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` FVU=0.1038\u3001r148 `two_stage_residual_expert` FVU=0.1140\u3001r149 `factorized_expert_topk` FVU=0.2450\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5df2\u6709 family \u4e0a\u505a\u5c40\u90e8\u626b\u53c2\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u5f88\u4f4e\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u66f4\u9002\u5408\u8865\u6700\u5c0f\u65b0\u539f\u578b\u3002"
research/history/logs/agent_action_0071.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":69,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的链路是：先做共享低维投影 h(x)，再做 router 选单个静态 expert 子库，再由该 expert 的小型 head 在低维空间上打分并做 local top-k，最后把 (e,i) 扁平化为静态库查表上的有限加权和；静态库本身不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容。兼容性先验在本轮保持清晰：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 与本轮新增的 `factorized_expert_topk` 都属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，只能留作历史参考，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r69 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EF=1` 与训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题：把 shared low-rank basis 放进 expert 内部 head，而不是放在 expert 外部做全局 trunk，是否能在不拉长 active path 的前提下形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。按当前 proxy 粗估，shared basis + active expert head 的 encoder 成本应仍落在约 0.3x 量级，配合 `K=160` 的部署成本后总成本预计仍在约 0.45x-0.5x 带，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 70 已经说明现有 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 EF=1 外置 trunk 原型不足以继续支撑低成本前沿。本轮不再补旧 family 的局部点，而是新增一个更贴近当前高信息量假设的最小原型 `factorized_expert_topk`，并以 r69 为 matched reference 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，验证“shared low-rank basis + routed expert head”是否优于纯 routed-only `expert_topk`。","self_review":"这满足单轮单变量约束：训练配置相对 r69 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。代码侧只在 `sparsify/` 内完成最小 family 接线，不新增 tunable，因此不需要改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。选择开新 family 而不是继续扫 `expert_topk` 的 K 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的局部旋钮，是因为当前提示已明确指出更高信息量方向在 expert-internal low-rank；继续围绕 EF=1 旧原型做小修小补的信息增量已经不足。主要风险是 auto `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 可能偏大或偏小，导致首轮结果更多反映默认宽度而非结构上限；但这正符合新 family 第一轮先看结构是否值得继续、而不是先调宽度的要求。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 71 优先新增 `factorized_expert_topk`，覆盖当前未实现但高优先级的 `shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head` 结构槽位。","首轮原型不新增 tunable，复用现有 `NUM_EXPERTS` 与 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 语义；训练配置相对 r69 仅切换 `ARCHITECTURE`，归因最干净。","必须按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成 whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string instantiate/forward/backward smoke，然后再把真实训练结果当作结构证据。","不兼容 family 继续排除在 active frontier 外；本轮比较对象只限兼容 family。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在与 r69 相近总成本下明显优于 routed-only `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只显式设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，测试共享 basis 宽度是否是该新结构的主控制旋钮。","如果它只小幅改善但仍明显弱于 `<0.5x` 最佳锚点，则下一轮可做 matched `K=128` 左移测试，判断这条新结构更适合低成本还是中成本带。","如果它没有改善或训练异常，则应快速归档该 family 的当前原型，并把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他兼容的新 MoE-like 方向，而不是继续在旧 EF=1 原型上做邻域微调。"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0093.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d E(x) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u8bbe |E(x)|=2\uff1b\u6bcf\u4e2a B_e={b_{e,i}} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u201c\u9009 2 \u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u67e5\u8868/top-k + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u67e5\u8868\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9\u5730\uff0c`factorized_expert_topk` \u53ea\u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u4e14\u6700\u8fd1\u591a\u8f6e matched probe \u5df2\u7a33\u5b9a\u504f\u5f31\uff1b`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar69\u2192r73\u2192r74 \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e routed-only `expert_topk` \u5728\u56fa\u5b9a `K=160` \u4e0b\u968f `NUM_EXPERTS` \u6269\u5bb9\u4ecd\u6709\u6b63\u6536\u76ca\uff0c\u4f46\u5f53\u524d\u4ecd\u53ea\u6fc0\u6d3b\u5355 expert\uff0c\u5c1a\u672a\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u5bb9\u91cf\u9971\u548c\u70b9\u662f\u5426\u5176\u5b9e\u53d7 active path \u8fc7\u77ed\u9650\u5236\u201d\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r74 \u53ea\u5c06 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS: 1 -> 2`\uff0c\u82e5\u5f53\u524d\u74f6\u9888\u662f\u5355 token \u53ea\u80fd\u8bbf\u95ee\u4e00\u4e2a\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 router \u5f88\u8f7b\u4e14\u603b\u5f62\u5f0f\u4ecd\u4e3a\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u6709\u9650\u548c\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0cFVU \u5e94\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 0.1243\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7ea6 total_cost=0.69x\uff08selection\u22480.53x\uff0cdeployment\u22480.16x\uff09\u7684\u53ef\u884c\u5e26\u5185\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684 MoE-like \u7ed3\u6784\u951a\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0093.json:20:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u91cd\u590d `factorized_expert_topk` \u7684 matched \u5bf9\u7167\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u56de\u5230\u65e7 family \u7684\u5c40\u90e8 K \u8f74\u3002\u4ee5 r74 \u4e3a reference\uff0c\u53ea\u52a0 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54 routed-only `expert_topk` \u7684\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u5173\u952e\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5f53\u524d\u6536\u76ca\u74f6\u9888\u5230\u5e95\u5728\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5728\u6bcf\u4e2a token \u53ea\u770b\u4e00\u4e2a expert \u7684\u8fc7\u77ed active path\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0093.json:36:      "`factorized_expert_topk` \u5728 r90-r92 \u7684 matched multi-expert probe \u4e0a\u7a33\u5b9a\u505c\u5728\u7ea6 FVU=0.2158\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e shared-basis scorer \u8fd9\u6761\u7ebf\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u5e94\u4e0b\u8c03\uff0c\u4e0d\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u5360\u7528\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u63a2\u7d22\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0093.json:62:    "description": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u91cd\u590d `factorized_expert_topk` \u7684 matched \u5bf9\u7167\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u56de\u5230\u65e7 family \u7684\u5c40\u90e8 K \u8f74\u3002\u4ee5 r74 \u4e3a reference\uff0c\u53ea\u52a0 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54 routed-only `expert_topk` \u7684\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u5173\u952e\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5f53\u524d\u6536\u76ca\u74f6\u9888\u5230\u5e95\u5728\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5728\u6bcf\u4e2a token \u53ea\u770b\u4e00\u4e2a expert \u7684\u8fc7\u77ed active path\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0097.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":95,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"112"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r95 (`K=128`) 与 r96 (`K=96`) 已经把当前有效主线 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 两端都测出来，但中间缺少 `K=112` 这个最关键的边界点。相对 r95 仅将 `K: 128 -> 112`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果当前质量退化主要发生在 `K<112` 之后，那么 `K=112` 应能明显优于 r96 的 0.1305，同时把 total_cost 从 r95 的同配方进一步左移到约 0.43x（按当前 fresh cost 粗估），从而完成 `K=96-128` 边界定位。","summary":"当前不要继续细扫 `TRUNK_RANK`，也不要回到 routed-only 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这些已给出负信号的方向。以 r95 为 reference，只改 `K=112`，把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 当前主线 recipe 的 `K=96-128` 压缩边界补完整；这是 operator guide 明确要求优先完成的 knee 定位步骤。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r95 只改 `K`。这不是 old-family 的普通 K 轴回退，因为当前 <0.5x 有效主线已经明确是 `lowrank_expert_topk`，且 r95/r96 正好留下一个高信息量的边界缺口。主要风险是 `K=112` 结果只是落在 r95 和 r96 的平滑插值线上而不形成新的非支配点；但即便如此，也能完成当前阶段明确要求的 `K=96-128` knee 定位，避免继续在未封口的边界上盲目切 family。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r95 (`lowrank_expert_topk TRUNK_RANK=40 K=128`) 与 r96 (`K=96`) 已证明当前低成本主线的 deployment budget 不是全-or-nothing，而是存在可继续压缩的空间。","当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴还缺少 `K=112` 这一中间点；补齐它比立即切去 `lowrank_expert_residual` 更符合 Round 97 的 runtime priority。","`factorized_expert_topk` 与 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 方向都已给出稳定负信号，本轮继续留在当前有效主线上更合理。","按当前 fresh cost 粗估，`lowrank_expert_topk K=112 NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=40` 的 selection 基本不变，deployment 低于 `K=128`，total_cost 约 0.43x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=112` 形成新的非支配中间点，则 `K=96-128` 边界已基本完成，下一轮应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 结构对照，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上细扫。","如果 `K=112` 基本贴着 r95-r96 的平滑插值且不形成新前沿，则说明当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 已足够清楚；下一轮同样应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`。","如果 `K=112` 意外明显劣化并接近 r96，则可判定当前主线对 deployment budget 比预期更敏感；下一轮应回到 `K=128` 配方，并优先测试 matched residual cleanup 是否值得其额外成本。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0097.stdout.log:203:  2. 防重复：如果同一 family 的同一结构假设连续 2 轮结果接近且未形成新非支配点，下一轮必须换轴或换 family；当前不要再重复 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1`。
research/history/logs/agent_round_0097.stdout.log:204:  3. 真正值得后续 code-edit 的新方向是 sparse-capacity expansion：`shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head/residual`。只有在现有 `lowrank_expert_topk` 主线完成 knee 定位、或连续无改进后，再新增 family；不要用 `factorized_expert_topk` 充当这个方向的长期替身。
