research/history/logs/agent_round_0146.stdout.log:648:r142_1774851648	1774851648	ok	discard	0.25618457794189453	112	shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0142/round0142_standard_1774851284_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k112_20260330_141451	22c62c1f3dc7430d6808298ccaaa37bbbea1b967			建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`。这是一轮低成本异构 MoE 结构重验：直接测试“shared+routed + expert 内部低秩 scorer”能否在约 0.22x total_cost 下提供比当前 low-cost frontier 更有价值的新段。	这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0142_standard_1774851284.log
